description:
Are you willing to take up the challenge of witnessing for Jesus?

God does not want you to miss the chance to be His witness. He wants you to be a channel of love, hope, and salvation for all people.

This #short clip from Pastor Ted Wilson’s weekly message demonstrates how God will unveil His amazing messages to every one of us as we study His Word to understand what will happen in the last days. God encourages every believer to be His witness in order to reach many people and share with them the salvation He offers.

Watch the full video to learn more about last-day events and how we can be a witness for Christ to everyone around us.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WHVy_xJAdnI&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=3


—---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Seventh-day Adventist Church has been an established denomination since 1863. It is a global Christian family with over 21 million members who hold the Bible as the ultimate authority. We are Christians who promise to help people understand the Bible to find freedom, healing, and hope in Jesus.
